OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice seize over #1 million of
OL,4,Ccocaine after stopping HGV
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged after police
OL,7,Fseized over #1 million of cocaine in
OL,8,FKent.
OL,10,FOfficers say a proactive stop of a
OL,11,Fsuspicious vehicle near Hythe led to
OL,12,Fthe seizure of almost 50kg of cocaine.
OL,14,FIt has an estimated street value of
OL,15,Fmore than #1 million.
OL,17,FOfficers from Folkestone's beat team
OL,18,Fwere on patrol on the A20 at around
OL,19,F10am on Thursday 21 May 2026 when they
OL,20,Fspotted an HGV that was being driven
OL,21,Fin a suspicious manner.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
