OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779962735
OL,3,CPolice seize over #1 million of
OL,4,Ccocaine after stopping HGV
OL,6,FFollowing a short pursuit, the vehicle
OL,7,Fwas brought to a stop and two men were
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of drugs
OL,9,Foffences.
OL,11,FLater searches led to the discovery of
OL,12,Fthree bags containing 46 blocks of
OL,13,Fwhite powder.
OL,15,FDzmitry Danilah, a 36 year old
OL,16,FBelarusian national of no fixed
OL,17,Faddress, and Klodian Marku, a 25 year
OL,18,Fold Albanian national of South Lambeth
OL,19,FRoad, Vauxhall, London, have since
OL,20,Fbeen charged with being concerned in
OL,21,Fthe importation of cocaine.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
