OL,3,CPolice seize over #1 million of
OL,4,Ccocaine after stopping HGV
OL,6,FBoth men were remanded in custody when
OL,7,Fthey appeared at Folkestone
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,10,FThey will next appear before
OL,11,FCanterbury Crown Court on 22 June 2026.
